Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time spent on 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Average resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time between 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' for cases that are eventually approved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total resolution time of cases involving 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and then 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' in cases followed by 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average waiting time to 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' from the start of the case
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Total time it takes 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' after 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' in cases that are eventually approved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimum time it takes from 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' in cases that are re-submitted and approved
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Request Payment' in successful re-submission cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Request Payment'
